transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra. Joanna speaking. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: I need to cancel my prescription.

Speaker 1: Can I get your name and date of birth, please?

Speaker 2: Tony Hoffman, 11-12-57.

Speaker 1: Okay, Mr. Hoffman.

Speaker 2: All right. I have your account pulled up here, sir.

Speaker 1: I am seeing that you are a VIP status customer

Speaker 2: and you've been with us for quite some time.

Speaker 1: What was the reason for the cancellation today?

Speaker 2: The increased cost.

Speaker 1: Okay. Let me see what you've been getting.

Speaker 2: So you've been getting 24 of the AGV for $53.95.

Speaker 1: And you're a VIP customer,

Speaker 2: so we've really given you a great price here for 24 of them.

Speaker 1: Now for 25 of them, it's $113.

Speaker 2: Yeah, I can get it cheaper through my own doctor.

Speaker 1: That makes sense.

Speaker 2: Have you tried the new AGV, Viagra?

Speaker 1: Have you heard of it?

Speaker 2: No, but I'm not interested. Thanks.

Speaker 1: No, of course.

Speaker 2: And I wasn't trying to sell you on anything.

Speaker 1: I know it sounded like I was.

Speaker 2: And as a matter of fact,

Speaker 1: because you've been such a loyal customer for so many years

Speaker 2: and you're a VIP,

Speaker 1: I wanted to send you a sample of 10 of them to try

Speaker 2: because it's the new and improved Viagra through Pfizer.

Speaker 1: So they just released it.

Speaker 2: So Viagra's been around for many years, as you know.

Speaker 1: And over time,

Speaker 2: they have made modifications primarily to the inactive ingredient,

Speaker 1: which affects the delivery mechanism.

Speaker 2: So it's more direct.

Speaker 1: It works faster.

Speaker 2: They've eliminated the common side effects people used to get.

Speaker 1: So our customers are really happy with it.

Speaker 2: And since you're a VIP customer,

Speaker 1: I can send you a sample of 10 of them to try and see what you think.

Speaker 2: This isn't something that you would be able to get from a doctor.

Speaker 1: It's exclusively through ScoreBlue.

Speaker 2: So I highly recommend you try it.

Speaker 1: It's got no risk, no cost to you.

Speaker 2: I can put your account on a hold for five months,

Speaker 1: and that way you can decide how you want to move forward.

Speaker 2: Okay, I'll try it.

Speaker 1: What's the cost of it?

Speaker 2: Well, this is going to be a courtesy,

Speaker 1: so obviously there's going to be a fair cost.

Speaker 2: I know, but beyond that.

Speaker 1: Ten of them would be $49.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: Yeah, I'll try the sample.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: I'll get that sent out to you,

Speaker 2: and you should get it in five days or less, okay?

Speaker 1: Okay, thank you.

Speaker 2: All right, sir.

Speaker 1: And my extension is 0024.

Speaker 2: I'm placing your account on a five-month hold

Speaker 1: and removing the monthly recurring refills,

Speaker 2: so you have an opportunity to really try out the HEV

Speaker 1: and then determine for yourself, okay?

Speaker 2: Okay, thank you.

Speaker 1: All right, thank you.

Speaker 2: Have a great day.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.

Speaker 2: Yep, you too.
